<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>مرتبعا<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>فَلَا نِكَاح بَيْننَا<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>فَهُوَ<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p22"></span>أَي الزَّوْج<a href="#p22" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p23"></span>مُدع<a href="#p23" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p24"></span>لِأَن وُقُوع الإسلاميين مَعًا خلاف الظَّاهِر وَهِي مدعى عَلَيْهَا وَلَكِن لما كَانَ الأَصْل بَقَاء الْعِصْمَة كَانَ القَوْل قَوْله فَيحلف وتستمر الْعِصْمَة<a href="#p24" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
